---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Bilingual from '../../components/Bilingual.astro';
import CodeTabs from '../../components/CodeTabs.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Array & String Problems · CS Notebook">
  <article class="space-y-6">
    <header>
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary-cyan mb-2">Problems / Array & String</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">
        <Bilingual><span slot="zh">数组与字符串题型</span><span slot="en">Array & String Problems</span></Bilingual>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
        <Bilingual>
          <span slot="zh">数组与字符串是最高频的考点。核心技巧：<b>哈希表</b>化查找为 O(1)、<b>双指针</b>压缩嵌套循环、<b>中心扩展</b>处理回文。下面精选三道经典题，覆盖这三种思路。</span>
          <span slot="en">Arrays and strings are the most frequently tested topics. Core techniques: <b>hash maps</b> turn lookups into O(1), <b>two pointers</b> flatten nested loops, <b>center expansion</b> handles palindromes. Three classic problems below cover these three ideas.</span>
        </Bilingual>
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">Two Sum（两数之和）</span><span slot="en">Two Sum</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh"><b>题意</b>：给定数组 nums 和目标值 target，返回和为 target 的两元素下标（恰有一解）。<b>思路</b>：暴力 O(n²) 会超时。用哈希表记录「值→下标」，遍历时查 <code>target - nums[i]</code> 是否已在表中：在则返回，不在则存入。一次遍历 O(n)。</span><span slot="en"><b>Problem</b>: Given array nums and target, return indices of two elements summing to target (exactly one solution). <b>Approach</b>: Brute O(n²) is too slow. Use a hash map "value→index"; for each i, look up <code>target - nums[i]</code>: if present, return; otherwise store nums[i]. One pass, O(n).</span></Bilingual></p>
      <CodeTabs
  cpp={`<pre><code>// Two Sum  O(n) 时间, O(n) 空间
vector&lt;int&gt; twoSum(vector&lt;int&gt;&amp; nums, int target) &#123;
    unordered_map&lt;int,int&gt; mp;          // 值 → 下标
    for (int i = 0; i &lt; nums.size(); i++) &#123;
        int need = target - nums[i];
        if (mp.count(need))
            return &#123;mp[need], i&#125;;   // 找到补数
        mp[nums[i]] = i;                 // 存当前值
    &#125;
    return &#123;&#125;;
&#125;</code></pre>`}
  py={`<pre><code># Two Sum  O(n) 时间, O(n) 空间
def two_sum(nums, target):
    mp = &#123;&#125;                       # 值 → 下标
    for i, x in enumerate(nums):
        need = target - x
        if need in mp:
            return [mp[need], i]   # 找到补数
        mp[x] = i                  # 存当前值
    return []</code></pre>`}
        />
    </section>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">Container With Most Water（盛水容器）</span><span slot="en">Container With Most Water</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh"><b>题意</b>：数组 heights 表示竖线高度，选两条线与 x 轴围成容器，求最大盛水量（面积 = min(h[i],h[j]) × (j-i)）。<b>思路</b>：相向双指针从两端出发。每步计算面积后，<b>移动较矮的一端</b>——因为面积受短板限制、宽度在缩小，只有让短板变高才可能更大。O(n) 一趟。</span><span slot="en"><b>Problem</b>: Array heights represents vertical lines; pick two lines with the x-axis to form a container; maximize water (area = min(h[i],h[j]) × (j-i)). <b>Approach</b>: opposing pointers from both ends. Compute the area, then <b>move the shorter end</b> — the area is bounded by the shorter board and the width is shrinking, so only raising the shorter board can help. O(n) one pass.</span></Bilingual></p>
      <CodeTabs
  cpp={`<pre><code>// 盛水容器  O(n)
int maxArea(vector&lt;int&gt;&amp; h) &#123;
    int lo = 0, hi = h.size() - 1, ans = 0;
    while (lo &lt; hi) &#123;
        int area = min(h[lo], h[hi]) * (hi - lo);
        ans = max(ans, area);
        if (h[lo] &lt; h[hi]) lo++;   // 移动较矮的一端
        else hi--;
    &#125;
    return ans;
&#125;</code></pre>`}
  py={`<pre><code># 盛水容器  O(n)
def max_area(h):
    lo, hi, ans = 0, len(h) - 1, 0
    while lo < hi:
        area = min(h[lo], h[hi]) * (hi - lo)
        ans = max(ans, area)
        if h[lo] < h[hi]: lo += 1  # 移动较矮的一端
        else: hi -= 1
    return ans</code></pre>`}
        />
    </section>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">Longest Palindromic Substring（最长回文子串）</span><span slot="en">Longest Palindromic Substring</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh"><b>题意</b>：求字符串 s 的最长回文子串。<b>思路</b>：中心扩展法。回文以中心对称，枚举每个位置作中心，分「奇数长度」（单字符中心）和「偶数长度」（双字符中心）两种向两边扩展，记录最长。共 2n-1 个中心，每次扩展 O(n)，总 O(n²)。比 DP 的 O(n²) 空间更省（O(1)）。</span><span slot="en"><b>Problem</b>: Find the longest palindromic substring of s. <b>Approach</b>: center expansion. A palindrome is symmetric about its center; enumerate each position as a center in two forms — "odd length" (single-char center) and "even length" (two-char center) — and expand outward, tracking the longest. 2n-1 centers, O(n) per expansion, total O(n²). Uses O(1) space — better than the O(n²)-space DP.</span></Bilingual></p>
      <CodeTabs
  cpp={`<pre><code>// 最长回文子串（中心扩展） O(n²) 时间, O(1) 空间
string longestPalindrome(string s) &#123;
    int n = s.size(), start = 0, maxLen = 1;
    for (int i = 0; i &lt; n; i++) &#123;
        // 奇数长度：单字符中心
        for (int l = i, r = i; l &gt;= 0 &amp;&amp; r &lt; n &amp;&amp; s[l] == s[r]; l--, r++)
            if (r - l + 1 &gt; maxLen) &#123; start = l; maxLen = r - l + 1; &#125;
        // 偶数长度：双字符中心
        for (int l = i, r = i + 1; l &gt;= 0 &amp;&amp; r &lt; n &amp;&amp; s[l] == s[r]; l--, r++)
            if (r - l + 1 &gt; maxLen) &#123; start = l; maxLen = r - l + 1; &#125;
    &#125;
    return s.substr(start, maxLen);
&#125;</code></pre>`}
  py={`<pre><code># 最长回文子串（中心扩展） O(n²) 时间, O(1) 空间
def longest_palindrome(s):
    n, start, max_len = len(s), 0, 1
    for i in range(n):
        # 奇数长度：单字符中心
        l, r = i, i
        while l >= 0 and r < n and s[l] == s[r]:
            if r - l + 1 > max_len:
                start, max_len = l, r - l + 1
            l -= 1; r += 1
        # 偶数长度：双字符中心
        l, r = i, i + 1
        while l >= 0 and r < n and s[l] == s[r]:
            if r - l + 1 > max_len:
                start, max_len = l, r - l + 1
            l -= 1; r += 1
    return s[start:start + max_len]</code></pre>`}
        />
    </section>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">数组字符串技巧速查</span><span slot="en">Array & String Techniques Cheatsheet</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="text-ink-muted text-left"><tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">技巧</span><span slot="en">Technique</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">要点</span><span slot="en">Key point</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">代表题</span><span slot="en">Representative</span></Bilingual></th></tr></thead>
          <tbody class="text-ink">
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted">哈希表</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">值→下标/计数，O(1) 查找</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">Two Sum、字母异位词</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted">相向双指针</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">两端向中间，移动短板</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">盛水容器、三数之和</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted">中心扩展</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">奇偶两种中心，向两边扩散</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">最长回文子串、回文计数</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted">前缀和</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">预处理 O(n)，区间和 O(1)</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">子数组和等于 K</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted">滑动窗口</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">维护连续区间，左右移动</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">最长无重复子串</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
